Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:07.02,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,In the State of Qin and the State of Wei's fierce battle, Xin and Lun Hu have faced off once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）秦国(しんこく)と魏国(ぎこく)との\N激戦の中で 再び対峙(たいじ)した信(しん)と輪虎(りんこ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:12.20,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Which one will be the one to surpass their limits and continue on their path?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:11.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界を超え 己の道を貫き通すのは\N果たして どちらか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:16.03,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,These two's heated emotions are now making sparks fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:16.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人の熱き思いが今 火花を散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:24.52,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Do you know just how important you are right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 背負っているものの重大さが\N分かっているかい？ 飛信(ひしん)隊の信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.09,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Xin of the Feixin Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:30.79,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,If you fall here, the entire State of Qin Army will collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:30.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）君が倒れれば\Nここの秦国軍は総崩れとなり―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:34.04,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,And we'll go take down Meng Ao in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:33.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは とっとと蒙驁(もうごう)を討ちに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.67,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit yammering!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ほざいてろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.67,0:00:41.52,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,If {\i1}you{\i0} get slain by {\i1}me{\i0}, then we'll win the central battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえのほうこそ 俺に討たれて\N中央の戦いは こっちの勝ちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:47.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャマが―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.39,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Everything that was in the way... is gone! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:49.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えた！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グアッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:12.08,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs90\be0.4\c&H000000&\pos(636,103)}A Single Moment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.61,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）信どのー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.97,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:23.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）信ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:27.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You bastaaard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）てめえー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.01,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,This is bad! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:29.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水(そすい)）マズイ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不安定な馬上での戦いには\N脚のふんばりが不可欠だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:32.05,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,On volatile horseback fights, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.37,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,keeping your legs braced is essential. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:40.55,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,If he's lost that, he can no longer stop Lun Hu's sword! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを失っては―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや 輪虎の剣は止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:44.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:57.89,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,And this... ends it. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.99,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂(こう)）信ーっ！\N（竜有(りゅうゆう)）隊長ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.03,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.61,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏良(ぎりょう)）将軍！\N（輪虎兵）輪虎さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.03,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.26,Kingdom-Main,Qi,0,0,0,,Not only did he stop that attack which he put everything he had into...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥(きょがい)）\N渾身(こんしん)の一撃を止められたうえに…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:49.89,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,If it becomes a ground battle with his leg like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永(でんえい)）よりによって あの脚で\N地上戦に もつれ込んだら…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:57.15,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,No. Lord Xin purposefully brought the battle to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）信どのは\Nわざと 地上戦に持ち込んだのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:12.16,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Honestly, you are quite the daredevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:08.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大胆だな 君は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:18.67,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,You saw yourself as being at a disadvantage on horseback, so you decided to take your chances on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:18.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬上では不利と見て イチかバチか\N地上戦に切り替えたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:25.39,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,That decision was not incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが その判断は間違っていない\Nあのまま続けてたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:31.14,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,If you'd continued as you were, this battle would have been over quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:31.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐにでも勝負は終わってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:39.29,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,However, my overwhelming advantage remains unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）…といっても 僕の\N圧倒的な有利は 変わらないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:46.35,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Can you even stand up with your leg like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも その脚で\N立ち上がれるのかい？ 飛信隊の信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.28,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Xin of the Feixin Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No fuckin' problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全く問題ねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:28.24,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Fighting with only one good leg
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:28.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,片足で戦わなきゃならねえ状況も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.74,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,is something Piao and I trained specially for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:31.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちり 漂(ひょう)と特訓済みだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウオーッ！ 信ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.75,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）\Nウオーッ！ 隊長ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.76,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.33,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,He's quite tenacious... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しぶとい… 一体 何なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:58.52,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Just what is this extraordinary strength of spirit he has? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この異常なほどの心の強さは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:03.02,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,What has been holding him up this whole time? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が彼をここまで支えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鬨(とき)の声）\N（２人）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:14.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？\N本陣で また何かあったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:14.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What? Did something happen at the headquarters again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.51,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, my lord. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すみません 殿… 少し お待ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.25,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Please, wait just a little longer. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.04,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I will be there soon.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに行きますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.68,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）射(う)てー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,射てー！ 射ちまくれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:40.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:51.45,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Send reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:51.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）応援を差し向けよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:56.05,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Gather all of the soldiers that are nearby the traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:55.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）ワナの\N周辺にいる全ての兵士を集めて―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:59.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一気に ここで勝負を決めよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.45,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,We will end this war in one final push!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:06.42,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,We must... We must take down Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず廉頗(れんぱ)をしとめるのじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:14.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Where is General Lian Po?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:19.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）廉頗将軍は どこだ？\Nなんとしても将軍をお守りしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Protect the general at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:24.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We can't! We can't even move right now! All we can do is try to shield ourselves from the arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）ダメだ　今は動けぬ\Nとにかく 矢をしのがねば…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:27.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Everyone, slip underneath!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:27.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員 下へ潜り込め！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're hiding underneath the corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:31.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,骸(むくろ)の下に隠れたぞ！\N投げ槍(やり) 出番だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.61,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Spearmen, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（槍の刺さる音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.88,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Where is Lian Po?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗は？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:54.38,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Did we take out Lian Po?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうなった？\N廉頗を討ち取ったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.84,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's hard to be sure of anything in this chaotic situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状況では\N確かなことは分からんが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:04.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Then we'll just keep shooting at anything that moves, and that will end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:02.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく 動く者が\N１人もいなくなるまで射ち続ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで おしまいだ\N（兵士）射て射て！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fire, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）ヌオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヌオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:30.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヌオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:40.68,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Knock every last soldier of the State of Qin Army down to the bottom of these cliffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:40.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国軍の兵士どもを １人残らず\N崖の下に たたき落としてやれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.69,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,This can't be... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなバカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:57.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The soldiers that were setting the traps have all been pushed down the cliffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:57.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）\Nワナを張っていた兵士たちが\N全て崖の下に突き落とされたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\N一体 どうなっておるのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What in the world is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:03.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,How did Lian Po appear on top of the cliffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:03.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬公）\Nなぜ 廉頗が崖の上に現れた？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:07.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wasn't he just caught in that trap and getting pelted with arrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）さっきまで あのワナに\Nハマって 矢を受けていたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.24,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,No. He was not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）いや そうではない\N（馬公）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:18.22,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,We assumed that because we saw the enemy's flag in that trap and Lian Po was there as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワナの中に敵の旗が見えたので―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:18.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗も 勝手に\Nそこにいるものと思い込んでいたが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:24.72,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,but on the path to that trap, there were some areas not visible to us from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワナに至るまでの道に―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:24.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらから死角になる場所が\Nなかったわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:28.73,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po split the soldiers under his command into two groups
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗は\N配下の兵士たちをふた手に分け―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:34.73,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,and led the group of soldiers he was leading onto a different path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:34.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分は 一方の兵士たちを率いて\N別の道を進んだのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:43.24,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And... the fact that he made such a move just before reaching the trap means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワナの直前で そのような行動を\N取ったということは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:49.03,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,that Lian Po even predicted this fortress's ace in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:48.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗は この砦(とりで)の奥の手をも\N読んでいたということじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:57.26,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,My plan... has not worked. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）わしの計略が―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:57.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通じなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.23,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Brilliant, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:06.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お見事です 殿\N（廉頗）半信半疑じゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.77,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I was only half convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.48,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The moment I perceived that the fortress was a maze
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:12.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,砦に迷路があると察した時点で―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを\N動かしてくる策があると思った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.90,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I thought there would be a plan to later shift it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:21.62,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,But in order to remake the paths to lead enemies into traps after they entered the maze
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:21.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 敵が迷路に入ってから\N道を作り替えて ワナにハメるには
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の動きを見定める目と―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:30.05,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,adept eyes for ascertaining the enemy's movements and to determine when ally soldiers should move were required.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:29.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,味方の兵を動かす時を決める\N高度な戦術の目が必要じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:41.08,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Even I doubted whether that mediocre general Meng Ao could've really set a troublesome trap like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしでも面倒な そんな戦術を―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:40.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの凡庸な蒙驁が\N本当に仕掛けてくるのかと疑ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:47.43,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,But just in case, I concocted a counter-strategy for places where it looked like traps were set.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:45.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念のため\Nワナが仕掛けてありそうな所では
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,対抗策を講じた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.58,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And the result is as it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果は このとおりよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:58.99,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Meng Ao, you old dog, you've held quite a grudge for all those losses against me and did some thorough preparation, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:55.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁め　わしに負け続けたことを\N相当 根に持って―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念入りに準備してきたようじゃのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:04.20,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,This fortress really is well constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:04.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この砦は本当に よくできているぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.50,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.23,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,even if you spent 40 years coming up with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,40年がかりで考えても―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:17.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしと知恵比べをするには\N百年早かったのぅ 蒙驁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:17.11,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,you're still 100 years too early to match wits against me, Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lian Po is coming to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）廉頗が攻め上ってくるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\Nバカな！ なぜ こうも簡単に…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.23,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Impossible! How did he get through so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:41.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Even if he escaped the traps, he should still be inside the maze!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:40.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワナを逃(のが)れたといっても\N迷路の中には いるはずなのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:45.49,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,He turned our plan to his advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:45.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらの作戦を\N逆手に取られたのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:50.88,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Since the maze was moved in order to trap Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:50.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗をワナに誘い込むために\N迷路を動かしたことで―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:55.50,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,many roads became easily passable roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:55.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくつかの道は\N素通りできる道となってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:11:03.65,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And furthermore, because we tried to focus our manpower around the traps in order to take out the enemy in one blow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に 一気に敵をたたくべく\Nワナの周囲に兵力を集中させたため
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守備の手薄な部分もできてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:07.01,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,we've created gaps in our defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:13.02,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po was most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗は 恐らく―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:16.02,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,targeting that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこをねらっていたのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:21.53,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I'm going to sprint straight to the peak, Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:21.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここからは 一気に\N駆け上がらせてもらうぞ 蒙驁！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:27.40,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I cannot... keep Lun Hu waiting! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:27.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎を待たせるわけには\Nいかんからのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:33.00,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs60\blur4\bord3\3c&HE1DFE0&\c&H010102&\pos(463.429,114.572)}Meng Ao
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:05.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）ヤーッ！\N（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:06.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充(りじゅう)）止められぬ…\N敵は もう８合目まで来ているぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:03.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They can't be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:06.59,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy's already reached the 8th level!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬公）殿！\N（馬令）廉頗が来ます！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:07.38,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lian Po is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:12.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）案ずるな　まだ８合目じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.93,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,No need to be concerned. It's only the 8th level!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:17.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この山頂まで２合分 残っておる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:17.54,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,There are still two more to the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:24.65,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,We no longer have any strategies like the maze at the middle levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:24.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや中腹に仕掛けた迷路のような\N策略はない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,基本に戻って 守備陣を整え\Nじっくり守るだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:29.55,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,So we just have to go back to basics. We will arrange a defensive formation and carefully protect ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:35.93,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,If we don't have a plan, Lian Po will have to face us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:35.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらに策がなければ その分\N廉頗も つきあわざるをえなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:41.52,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,He has no choice but to make his way here by attacking each and every defensive formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:41.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつひとつ 守備陣を攻略して\N上ってくるしか手がない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）\Nしかしながら 殿　それでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.57,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But my lord, even if he does have those obstacles...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬公）廉頗の あの勢いでは\Nここまで来るのは時間の問題です！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:49.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,With the momentum he has, it's only a matter of time until Lian Po reaches us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.83,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,A matter of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間の問題か…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.58,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,That's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:05.34,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,That is truly the Meng Ao Army's way of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:05.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それこそ正に蒙驁軍の戦い方である
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:09.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近たち）アア…\N（蒙驁）落ち着いて思い返してみよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.71,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Calm down and think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:15.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この蒙驁軍は わしと２人の副将が\N率いる３つの軍からなる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:15.96,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The Meng Ao Army is made up of three armies led by me and two vice generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:20.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれの軍の役割は\N単純 かつ 明快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:20.35,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The roles of those armies are simple and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:26.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この本軍は 大将のわしが\N討たれぬように ひたすら守り
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:26.36,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The main army's purpose is to protect me, the Great General, from being slain at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:32.81,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,And in the meantime, both vice generals attack the enemy Great General.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:32.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その間に どちらかの副将の軍が\N敵の大将を討ち取る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:37.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが わしらが\N常に勝利を収めてきた戦術じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:37.87,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,That is the strategy that has always won me victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:42.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But... Wang Jian is halted at that rear fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）しかし\N王翦(おうせん)は 後方の砦に足止めされ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎(かんき)に至っては\Nいまだ行方知れずです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:46.13,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,and Huan Ji's location is still unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:54.13,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,If we have lost track of Huan Ji, then that means our enemies have lost track of him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,味方の わしらが\N見失っているということは―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:54.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵も\N桓騎を見失っているということだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:03.65,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Believing that it {\i1}can{\i0} be and defending ourselves is our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その“まさか”を信じて守るのが\Nわしの戦じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.69,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Pan You! Send reinforcements to the right unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁(おうほん)）\N番陽(ばんよう)！ 右の部隊の援護に行け
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままでは 敵に突破されるぞ\N（番陽）しかし 賁さま…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:28.01,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,We're going to ride this momentum and break through the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.80,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,But Lord Ben...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは俺が なんとかする　急げ！\N（番陽）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.80,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,I will take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.95,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刺す音）\Nウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:41.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\Nウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎だけに\N警戒が集中しないよう―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:49.94,Kingdom-Thought,Ben,0,0,0,,We have gathered the elite fighters in our units so not all of the enemy's attention is focused on Lun Hu, but... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらの部隊に\N精鋭を集めているのだろうが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.57,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Today's State of Wei Army is abnormally strong. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:57.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬(もうてん)）\N今日の魏国軍は 異常に強い…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:05.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人たりとも生きて帰さぬぞ！\N秦国の侵略者ども！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:05.33,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't let a single one of those\N State of Qin invaders leave alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.38,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるよ あんたらにとっても\N負けられない戦だってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:10.71,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,This is a war you guys can't afford to lose.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:21.85,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,I really can't afford to leave my position in conditions like this. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:21.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに この状況じゃ\N持ち場を離れるわけには いかない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:25.32,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Please hold out, Xin! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとか持ちこたえてくれ 信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.74,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,That's it! He's at his limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ… もう限界だ！\N（慶(けい)）信を助けに行くぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:27.04,Kingdom-Main,Qing,0,0,0,,We're going to save Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）待て！\N（尾平）あっ… 楚水副長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.33,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.04,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Vice Captain Chu Shui?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:34.79,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,If we interfere now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで我々が手を出せば 信どのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:40.05,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Lord Xin will be rescued from his inferior position by his underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:39.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一騎打ちで劣勢になったところを\N部下に助けられたことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:44.36,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,For Lord Xin, a man with the goal of becoming the greatest general under the heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:44.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 天下の大将軍を\N目指す信どのにとっては―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:47.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生 消すことのできぬ汚点に\Nなりかねないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:47.56,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,it will be a stain on his life he'll never be able to erase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:51.31,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,But if he dies here, it all goes up in smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:51.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって\Nここで死んじまったら何もかもが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.81,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,He won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にはせぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:57.82,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Our captain... will not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らの隊長は 死にはせぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.52,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渕さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:23.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）一瞬だ… 一瞬でいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:24.21,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,A single moment. Just one moment is all I need. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:35.21,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,If Lun Hu leaves an opening... in that instant... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:34.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎が隙を見せたら その一瞬で…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.68,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll finish him! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しとめる！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.26,Kingdom-Thought,Wei,0,0,0,,I know... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏良）\N分かっておる… 武将にとって―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:59.26,Kingdom-Thought,Wei,0,0,0,,just how important a one-on-one fight is to the commander... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:58.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一騎打ちが どれほど重いものか\N十分 分かっておる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:06.26,Kingdom-Thought,Wei,0,0,0,,But far more important... is what we are embracing! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが今は それより重大なものを\N我々は抱えておる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.97,Kingdom-Thought,Wei,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Lord Lun Hu! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お許しを 輪虎どの！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Wei Liang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）魏良どの！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.66,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,I won't complain if I'm slain by you afterwards. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:18.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとで貴殿に斬られても文句はない\N我らは負けるわけにはいかぬのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.40,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,We cannot lose this! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.78,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,We cannot! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:21.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.63,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,That youngster still has fight in his eyes. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの小僧の目は死んでいない\Nこいつは―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:28.66,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,He is... dangerous! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:27.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,危険だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.49,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どのー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:42.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャマするな 秦国の犬がー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.80,Kingdom-Main,Wei,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way, you State of Qin dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏良）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）そこからは\N正に 刹那の出来事であった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:19:00.55,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,What happened next was truly an ephemeral event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 郭備(かくび)の敵(かたき)を目の前にした\N抑え難き衝動だったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:20.06,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,With vengeance for Gui Bei right in front of him, perhaps it was too difficult for him to curb his impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:25.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,または\N楚水本人の自己防衛本能だったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:25.56,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Or perhaps it was Chu Shui's instinct\N for his own self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:31.47,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Either way, Chu Shui had a momentary burst of intense bloodlust
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:31.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく 瞬間的に\N湧き起こった楚水の強烈な殺意が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:34.60,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and aimed towards Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎に向かったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:40.40,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Lun Hu reflexively cut him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:40.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎は反射的に それを斬った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:46.74,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,For that fleeting instant, his attention was drawn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:46.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 己への注意が\N外れた まばたきほどの瞬間を…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:07.76,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,I felt... a response! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手応えは あった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:19.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It can't be! Lord Lun Hu was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）\Nそんなバカな　あの輪虎さまが…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:21.77,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:22.72,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Vice Captain Chu Shui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.78,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グアッ…\N（輪虎）ウッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.62,Kingdom-Main,Qi,0,0,0,,That bastard! He's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:34.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの野郎 まだ…\N（昂）大丈夫か？ 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.54,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Xin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.22,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騒ぐな！ 最後の あがきってやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This is just his final struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:43.95,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,He can't... get up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは もう―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち上がれねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:47.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち上がれるはず… が…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,There's no way he... can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立った あの傷で…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.84,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.41,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,With that wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:04.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジでバケモノか？ あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:04.47,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Is he... seriously a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.70,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu. You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎 てめえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:19.21,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,My lord is... waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:18.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿が… 待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:24.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所で負けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:24.84,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I cannot... lose here.
